sources.title: Loon Lake | Full Horror Thriller Movie | Minnesota Ghost
sources.description:
Loon Lake - Eager to escape the grief and nightmares of the city, Louis Olsen travels to Southwest Minnesota, seeking the peace of the rural countryside. When he accidentally disturbs the grave of a supposed local 'witch' Mary Jane Terlinden, what began as a peaceful reprieve unravels into a haunting nightmare from which Louis cannot escape - but is it all just in his head?
2019.  Stars: Nathan Wilson, David Selby, Kelly Erin Decker
